{"tid":1243016,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以武力爭取撤銷暴動罪有一個邏輯問題係度","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T10:34:25.000Z","uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"000a3ef69ea6c92ae7d3bcea91c7bd8a01f62069","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"到底要點樣先有機會令政府撤銷暴動罪檢控呢? 兩個方向<br />\n<br />\nA. 讓政府及大眾認同 我地大部份係和平理性非暴力 經過上星期之後 失地表達意見使用武力變得非常克制<br />\n<br />\nB. 以武力威脅 若不銷罪 官逼民反 我們便會認為武力升級合理<br />\n<br />\nC. 其它<br />\n<br />\n你認為?"},{"pid":"3086ed528596776cb578b4d5f257aeb5bc8a9720","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"*我地表達意見使用武力變得非常克制"},{"pid":"959663490f9c0d43bed14ae7f8198a96b5590ea6","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"呢件事亦會牽涉到 懲治黑警 問題<br />\n<br />\n無合理原因下武力升級<br />\n一般市民可能會諗 黑警未必錯晒"},{"pid":"ddbfc0fc58bb8e03a8fca5a4fc6cad251e77fb1b","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"你地如果打算從武力升級方向出發<br />\n對於我們去爭取 撤銷暴動檢控 <br />\n爭取懲罰黑警 改革警察制度<br />\n必然牽涉到上述問題<br />\n不能做了才算"},{"pid":"3a1672a5755de4e55171953cbd2a25d436765ff8","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b99ba0b5fd2d38d6a6518d9f92c103319e6880a","tid":1243016,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"有咩邏輯問題？"},{"pid":"387ae16e78d7963579b92236724b066aaab51475","tid":1243016,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b99ba0b5fd2d38d6a6518d9f92c103319e6880a","tid":1243016,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"有咩邏輯問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"以武力爭取撤銷暴動罪<br />\n即係